<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
    <head>
        <title>Create your Journey</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/styles.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/forms.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/grid.css">
        <script src="js/form.js"></script>
        <script src="js/burgermenu.js"></script>
        <style>
            textarea {
                width: calc(100% - 20px);
                padding: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                resize: vertical;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body id="containerbody">
        <%- include("includes/header.ejs") %>
        <%- include("includes/nav.ejs") %>
        <main id="containermain">
            <h2>Creating a new Recommendation</h2>
            <form action="http://localhost:8020/CreateRecommendation" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <fieldset>
                    <legend>Recommendation informations</legend>
                    <label for="description">Add your favourites</label>
                    <textarea id="description" name="description" cols="30" rows="10" minlength="40" maxlength="1000" placeholder="What would you like to do?"></textarea>
                    <label for="antwort1">1. What are your interests or hobbies that you would like to incorporate into your vacation? (e.g., nature, art, music, sports)</label>
                    <textarea name="antwort1" id="antwort1" rows="4"></textarea>
                    <label for="antwort2">2. Do you prefer active holidays (such as hiking, cycling, skiing etc.) or more relaxing holidays (e.g., at the beach, wellness experiences)?</label>
                    <textarea name="antwort2" id="antwort2" rows="4"></textarea>
                    <label for="antwort3">3. Do you have a preference for the climate or weather at your vacation destination? (e.g., warm, cold, dry, humid)</label>
                    <textarea name="antwort3" id="antwort3" rows="4"></textarea>
                    <label for="antwort4">4. Are there any specific regions or countries you are interested in, or would like to avoid?</label>
                    <textarea name="antwort4" id="antwort4" rows="4"></textarea>
                    <label for="antwort5">5. Would you prefer an urban, suburban, or rural setting for your vacation destination?</label>
                    <textarea name="antwort5" id="antwort5" rows="4"></textarea>
                    <label for="antwort6">6. What activities do you enjoy? (e.g., hiking, museums, surfing)</label>
                    <textarea name="antwort6" id="antwort6" rows="4"></textarea>
                    <label for="antwort7">7. Are you looking for adventurous experiences like bungee jumping or skydiving?</label>
                    <textarea name="antwort7" id="antwort7" rows="4"></textarea>
                    <label for="antwort8">8. When do you plan to go on vacation, and how flexible are your dates?</label>
                    <textarea name="antwort8" id="antwort8" rows="4"></textarea>
                    <label for="antwort9">9. Will you be traveling alone, or will others be joining you? If others are joining, how many people, and what are their preferences and interests?</label>
                    <textarea name="antwort9" id="antwort9" rows="4"></textarea>
                    <label for="language">In which language do you like your answer?</label>
                    <select id="language" name="language" required size="4">
                        <option value="de">German</option>
                        <option value="en">English</option>
                        <option value="es">Spanish</option>
                        <option value="fr">French</option>
                    </select><span></span><br><br>
                </fieldset>
                <fieldset>
                    <legend>Time for travel</legend>
                        <label for="date">Startdate</label>
                        <input id="date" name="date" type="date" size="20" required><span></span><br><br>
                        <label for="date">Enddate</label>
                        <input id="date" name="date" type="date" size="20" required><span></span><br><br>
                        <label for="submit">Create Recommendation</label>
                        <input id="submit" value="LetÂ´s go!" type="submit">
                </fieldset>
            </form>
        </main>
        <%- include("includes/aside.ejs") %>
        <%- include("includes/footer.ejs") %>
    </body>
</html>